title: Lost Moo
description:
Lost Moon: The Perilous Voyage of Apollo 13
Book by Jeffrey Kluger and Jim Lovell

Lost Moon: The Perilous Voyage of Apollo 13, is a non-fiction book first published in 1994 by astronaut James Lovell and journalist Jeffrey Kluger, about the failed April, 1970 Apollo 13 lunar landing mission which Lovell commanded. 

Originally published: 1994
Authors: Jeffrey Kluger, Jim Lovell
Genres: Non-fiction
Adaptations: Apollo 13 (1995)
Country: United States of America
Subjects: Aerospace Engineering



format: .mobi
